'''Ardis Butterfield''' is the [[Marie Borroff]] Professor of English and Professor of Music and French at [[Yale University]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Ardis Butterfield {{!}} Department of Music|url=http://yalemusic.yale.edu/people/ardis-butterfield|website=yalemusic.yale.edu|publisher=Yale University|accessdate=17 July 2017|language=en}}</ref>

Butterfield co-founded the Medieval Song Network.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ardis Butterfield {{!}} English|url=http://english.yale.edu/people/tenured-and-tenure-track-faculty-professors-staff/ardis-butterfield|website=english.yale.edu|publisher=Yale University|language=en}}</ref>

